&lt;p&gt;We’re a startup… so a self-starter mentality comes first and foremost. You are someone who will dive into whatever challenge is placed in front of you, and find creative ways to solve problems by evaluating multiple courses of action and determining appropriate resolution paths within established operational and regulatory frameworks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;What Will You Be Doing?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
