&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and deliver ongoing regular reporting and analysis for executive leadership, focused on high-impact strategic initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform ROI analysis across teams, platforms, tools, products, and features to guide organizational priorities and investments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with FP&amp;amp;A to manage commission structures, quotas, and related financial workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze the sales cycle using data-driven insights to recommend process improvements and efficiency gains.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop visual analytics (e.g., heat maps) to evaluate the current book of business versus total addressable market and identify areas for growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and maintain scalable dashboards and reporting tools in platforms like Salesforce, Tableau, and/or Sigma.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Draft strategic planning documentation to highlight key analysis including strategic memos, presentation decks, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
