&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;The Necessities&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced Excel skills, with the ability to work with large datasets and build dynamic models.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience building reporting within and extracting data from Salesforce.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Tableau and/or Sigma (preferred).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background in consulting and/or financial services strategy (highly preferred).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
