&lt;li&gt;Practice a proven and successful sales methodology (MEDDPICC).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Successfully hit KPIs month over month; inclusive of but not limited to successfully meeting your quota and hitting your key performance indicator metrics MoM.&lt;/li&gt;
