&lt;li&gt;Process invoices and payments to state agencies in accordance with contractual terms and internal approval workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain up-to-date reference documentation for all client contracts and fee schedules, updating as agreements are executed or amended.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collect proper approvals for revenue calculation packages prior to submission.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
